.TH "LIGHTNING-NODE-ONCHAIN-BALANCE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-node-onchain-balance \- show confirmed and unconfirmed on-chain balance
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning node-onchain-balance
.SH DESCRIPTION
Returns the on-chain Bitcoin balance from CLN's
.B listfunds
RPC, split by confirmation status.
.PP
Output:
.nf
{"confirmed_sat":N,"unconfirmed_sat":N,"total_sat":N}
.fi
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-node-funds (1),
.BR lightning-node-mempool (1)
